included.description:
Worked with the City of Jackson and a local public relations firm to design and build a website that illustrates the large construction project in downtown Jackson, MI. The team and I designed the website creating low, medium and high fidelity prototypes.  We also established a business registry so that local owners know how to find additional information about the project and how it effects their business. 

Featured on University of Michigan School of Information website: 
https://www.si.umich.edu/news/umsi-students%E2%80%99-website-allows-jacksonians-track-downtown-reconstruction
